ISLAMABAD, May 24 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan on Monday expressed his deep grief and sorrow over the sad demise of Liaquat Khan, the brother of Minister for Aviation Ghulam Sarwar Khan.
The Prime Minister prayed for the departed soul and conveyed his condolences to the bereaved family.
